                Gestionar Keywords
            </a>
            <a href="https://ruta11app.agenterag.com/jobs/" target="_blank" class="flex items-center gap-3 px-3 py-2 text-sm text-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-50 rounded-lg transition-colors">
